OL,3,COnboard the fully autonomous boat that
OL,4,Ccould save lives at sea
OL,6,FWe joined as the USV - an uncrewed
OL,7,Fautonomous boat - is in its testing
OL,8,Fphase, with two sailors controlling
OL,9,Fthe throttle.
OL,11,FBut as we head out beyond the harbour
OL,12,Fwalls, it's time for the crew to leave
OL,13,Fthis 1500 horsepower boat, and for the
OL,14,Fautonomous computer to take control.
OL,16,FIt can drive and steer itself up to
OL,17,Fspeeds of 70 miles per hour.
OL,19,FThough they're currently working on
OL,20,Fits ability to park and dodge debris
OL,21,Fand other vessels.
