OL,3,COnboard the fully autonomous boat that
OL,4,Ccould save lives at sea
OL,6,FThe hope is that autonomous boats can
OL,7,Fbe used for jobs which are dirty, dull
OL,8,For dangerous. It could mean the saving
OL,9,Fof man hours and, in some cases, lives
OL,10,Fthemselves.
OL,12,FThe team tells me that such vessels
OL,13,Fcould be deployed on long surveillance
OL,14,Fpatrols; heading out in rough seas, or
OL,15,Fdelivering marines to battlefields.
OL,17,FBut there is always a human ready to
OL,18,Ftake control.
