OL,3,COnboard the fully autonomous boat that
OL,4,Ccould save lives at sea
OL,6,FTo avoid a Terminator-style takeover,
OL,7,Fthe autonomous system can be turned
OL,8,Foff at any time - or even switched to
OL,9,Fremote control.
OL,11,FAnd while it's being designed
OL,12,Fspecifically for the military - in
OL,13,Ftheory, the kit can be fitted to any
OL,14,Fsimilar sized vessel.
OL,16,FIt's hoped in time this portal tech
OL,17,Fcould can help in search and rescue at
OL,18,Fsea and even allow Border Force to
OL,19,Fbetter police the English Channel.
